'''African-American <!-- "African American" is a noun, "African-American" is an adjective --> leftism''' refers to [[Left-wing politics|left-wing]] political currents that have developed among various [[African-American]] communities in the [[United States of America]]. These currents are active around social issues, and often call for an expansive state that aims at bringing about [[equality of outcome]] between the [[African-American]] community and [[White people|White]] community and other minority groups. {{Citation needed|date=October 2007}}

